Question: One of the images features exactly three musicians.

Reference Answer: False

Original program:

```
ANSWER0=VQA(image=LEFT,question='How many musicians are in the image?')
ANSWER1=VQA(image=RIGHT,question='How many musicians are in the image?')
ANSWER2=EVAL(expr='{ANSWER0} == 3 or {ANSWER1} == 3')
FINAL_ANSWER=RESULT(var=ANSWER2)
```
